short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get INSTANT answers to homework, quizzes, and tests. Private. ALL websites work including Canvas, BlackBoard, McGrawHill, D2L

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Want to get answers and study help in a click? Get INSTANT answers with homeworkhelper+. 
Never have to search for answers again. HomeworkHelper+ gives you answers to your homework, quiz, and test questions directly on your screen with the click of a button. NEW HIGHLIGHT/RIGHT CLICK & ASK FEATURE is universal It's even free to download and try out! Take it for a test drive. 

SOME people have reported problems seeing/using the extension, make sure you "refresh" after you download to ensure it works. 

You see, it uses datasets and AI to get the right answer and display it on your screen. It's smart. It's passed AP exams, the bar exam, and medical exam with flying colors. Pass with ease = no stress. If you are interested in checking yourself or getting answers, then this could be for you. 

It works on all question types: Multiple choice, true or false, it even will provide answers for essay / free response questions. NEW RIGHT CLICK & ASK FEATURE is universal and works on all platforms and websites (including Canvas, McGrawHill, Blackboard, Moodle, D2L, and more).

The extension is downloaded right on your web browser so it is private and discrete (no one will know unless you tell them) so no need to worry about privacy. 

So, if you're interested in getting answers or using it to check your gut, go ahead and download Homework Helper+ by clicking the "add to chrome" button above now.

So go ahead and give it a go. You could be using it in less than 30 seconds from now. 

Simple click the "add to chrome" on this screen now. We hope you like it (but are pretty confident you will based on our current student reviews and customer service:) ) Our team is here to help with any questions that come up (we send a video tutorial after you download it). See you on the other side!
